Our requirements:
• 7 years of experience;
• Good experience mainly in: Power BI (front and backend), Data Bricks using SQL and Python, Azure Data Factory, Azure Data Lake, Azure Analytics;
• Experience working with CI/CD;
• Experience working with Azure, or any cloud technology (for example: AWC/GCP);
• Very good communication skills in English (written and spoken);
• Nice to have: experience in working with infrastructure as code in Terraform framework, data modelling for data science, have a developer background who wants to move int to data and analytics, engineering knowledge.

Position: Senior Data Engineer (Power BI)
Location: Cracow, Lesser Poland, Poland (work in hybrid)

What type projects you work with:
• Projects with data products for data and analytics: data sourcing and exploration, data pipelining and end products primarily in Power BI.
